Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是多洛莫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:48.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從我等神明手上搶走的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.33,0:00:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由多種禁忌的技術製成的破壞型兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:00:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再這樣下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告全軍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:15.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請立即撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就能鎮壓城堡了 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.11,0:01:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能繼續在此地戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.49,0:01:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即回神界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:26.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.82,0:01:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類已經是苟延殘喘之輩了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.53,0:01:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不立即撤退啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.20,0:01:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕貝有我們幾個他行 先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.71,0:01:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒救出媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然從戰場中央冒出來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之先去個避人耳目的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:00.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 麗塔 你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有種不祥的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手 艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跟我們一起逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法瓦羅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類的王在那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,殺了人類的王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:29.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去會全滅的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:52.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別殺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別殺了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.37,0:09:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法瓦羅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.79,0:09:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只看見他飛得超快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.55,0:09:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知妮娜被吹到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.43,0:09:57.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你成功逃獄了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼睛...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:07.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩一隻也能看見你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身為國王 竟然挑起戰爭 把城市都毀了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.12,0:10:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還跟我跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還想跳舞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得去救他們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:34.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們已經逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:43.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.56,0:10:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫你？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:06.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱住我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱住我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你抱住我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我能變成龍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:06.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貞德大人 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.03,0:17:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別隨便碰裸體女士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路過的殭屍而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以為我會放跑你們？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.81,0:17:46.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走麗塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:55.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就這麼關心飛走的爆炸頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:58.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別死了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:34.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別殺死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神已被擊退了 先這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回城堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.21,0:18:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾爾依然處於昏迷狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為何人類的王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能找到那東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個破壞型兵器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.48,0:19:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個技術出現在米斯塔爾西還沒有人神魔的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即舊世界的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.37,0:19:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便從我等手中奪走了石板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:29.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類根本不可能擁有將其拼接起來的知識
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個兵器擁有打破世界的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將世界引向滅亡的為量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像巴哈姆特一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 我沒闖禍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 多虧了妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,0:21:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 凱撒和師傅被拋下了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:41.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我去看看情況
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？等...太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妮娜 你陪著聖女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.48,0:21:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別回王都哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:21:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是罪犯加越獄犯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.36,0:21:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麗塔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.03,0:21:59.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回王都
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看凱撒和爆炸頭過得怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:06.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜 妮娜交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.12,0:22:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 麗塔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去神界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.18,0:22:30.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.14,0:22:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的戰爭 我看見艾爾了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.81,0:22:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個光芒是艾爾的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.36,0:22:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姆伽羅妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.74,0:22:45.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退的眾神應該回神界了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是目前唯一與艾爾有關的線索
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我不知道神界的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.83,0:22:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 搞不好有辦法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.25,0:22:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.30,0:23:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此話當真？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.92,0:23:06.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得故鄉的奶奶說過以前經常去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:07.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故鄉？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.35,0:23:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.89,0:23:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 去妮娜的故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.82,0:23:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸？可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.82,0:23:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒有別的線索了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.79,0:23:36.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衝啊 駿鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:49.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,見識到多洛莫斯的力量了吧 石頭的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.64,0:23:53.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與我同步 變成手的形狀 biubiubiu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.31,0:23:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簡直颯爽得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:23:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 神擊的巴哈姆特 Virgin Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.35,0:23:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.52,0:24:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,biubiubiu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.91,0:24:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴哈巴哈巴哈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.25,0:24:10.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下週還要看哦
